==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Perkinism
<hw>Per"kin*ism</hw> <pr>(p⟦etil⟧r"k⟦icr⟧n*⟦icr⟧z'm)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>A remedial treatment, by drawing the pointed
extremities of two rods, each of a different metal, over the affected
part; tractoration, -- first employed by <person>Dr. Elisha
<etsep>Perkins</etsep></person> of Norwich, Conn. See
<er>Metallotherapy</er>.</def> <mark>[archaic]</mark> ⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Perky</ent>⟦br⟧
